### Recommendations Microservice API Tests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:2000

### 1. Get Personalized Recommendations for a User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recommendations/personalized-recommend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "f8a9b0c1-d2e3-4f5a-8b9c-0d1e2f3a4b5c",
  "query": "Looking for premium audio and tech gadgets",
  "preferences": "High quality audio, long battery life, premium build quality",
  "category": "electronics"
}

